{"tid":5031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屋企人思想好守舊，正一怪獸家長","createTime":"2016-11-26T17:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T18:01:56.000Z","uid":6795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"972fd6c4cfbabcdc56910278867f7a4d53a2b43a","tid":5031,"uid":6795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:30:43.000Z","msg":"各位請幫幫小弟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企係大家族黎嘅，我啲親戚個個都係子承父業。而我就由細到大已經比佢地管住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地乜都唔比我做，每日就係讀書、溫習、上興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係想好似同其他同齡嘅小朋友一樣過一個開心嘅童年姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次同佢地講我嘅夢想，就個個出黎反對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打擊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話咁樣姐係同佢地作對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到底我可以點做？<br />\n點先可以說服到佢地俾我出去實踐夢想？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a4825e5c7d328a530628600198e16220d03168","tid":5031,"uid":1592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:31:47.000Z","msg":"靠自己養自己"},{"pid":"cdd7c75c8c618ecd12e3f0b038986dbf034eadc3","tid":5031,"uid":12842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:36:12.000Z","msg":"請問你幾歲？讀緊咩？夢想係咩？"},{"pid":"59b6a2f1fa1081bb34c8e148e8c4febfefec1469","tid":5031,"uid":6795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠自己養自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我打算由零開始，慢慢捱上去，應該可以成功"},{"pid":"55f1cf50a27a63a301ba0c51f894deaf2cc93cde","tid":5031,"uid":6795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:41:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問你幾歲？讀緊咩？夢想係咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今年18歲，讀緊魔王課程，我夢想係要做勇者。"},{"pid":"557184e5436c525c79753a19f413b83ddcfee532","tid":5031,"uid":12570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"要做勇者唔係咁易架喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ed2349e400e32ce8bf83dece422f2082ddf3b8","tid":5031,"uid":6795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要做勇者唔係咁易架喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係我都唔想就咁比人睇死"},{"pid":"7976944e23316c04e4124e34e7d873309da117fe","tid":5031,"uid":27068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:52:55.000Z","msg":"拿 首先你要證明你已經大個仔 <br />\n已經有能力自立門戶<br />\n證明到之後 無理由唔俾啦<br />\n利申：我除完褲證明自己大個仔之後 屋企人即刻趕我出去"},{"pid":"8823255b4db64d05713ec32d349a0c6831c6ee5c","tid":5031,"uid":6795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿 首先你要證明你已經大個仔 <br />\n已經有能力自立門戶<br />\n證明到之後 無理由唔俾啦<br />\n利申：我除完褲證明自己大個仔之後 屋企人即刻趕我出去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家係狩獵史萊姆方都略有所成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都希望可以盡快證明到自己係有能力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}